CD
) originate from posteromesal region of spermathecae (Fig. 12 
D
). CD path direct, gently curved or sinuous, running posteriorly from spermathecae (Fig. 8 
B
). FD relatively robust, gently curved, running posteriorly from spermathecae (Fig. 8 
B
).
